({literal})
&lt;img src="https://px.a8.net/cgi-bin/a8fly/sales?pid=s0001&amp;so=<strong>({$ID})</strong>&amp;si=000.000.A8&amp;ts=<strong>({$DATETIME})</strong>"<br>
